{"tid":24138,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港再辦英超盃味濃 惟兩日賽不再 勢被中國分餅","createTime":"2016-12-05T11:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T02:09:59.000Z","uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"644921282aa307093a921d2cb8985e0136c8033d","tid":24138,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:19:52.000Z","msg":"薛基輔：有信心英超挑戰盃明年7月回歸香港<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=fd4f8c7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 足總行政總裁薛基輔周一（12月5日）透露，目前一直就英超亞洲挑戰盃與英超賽會協商，雖然一切未有定案，但有信心賽事明年7月下旬，會第4度在港上演，倘一切順利，預計會在1月正式「報喜」，若然落實在港舉行，預計會於7月22日上演。<br />\n<br />\n不過薛指，英超亞洲挑戰盃明年倘再度在港舉行，將有別於以往分兩個賽日進行的模式，改為中國及香港兩地分別舉行1個賽日，但依舊有3支英超球隊參賽，3隊都會在兩個賽日登場；香港則會派出今季港超聯冠軍球隊參賽。"},{"pid":"4379a72cb0fb4eb2de8071831e64703e15237037","tid":24138,"uid":48659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"咁會唔會順帶宣傳埋香港足球？"},{"pid":"f70384405192dbb6108ebc56a5629b92bcd3c3ef","tid":24138,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"食屎狗支那"},{"pid":"906f09b2d238e99e14300674e3e25cb45def5b96","tid":24138,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"中國及香港兩地分別舉行1個賽日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b35c264a3c521ebe35cc67c23f3da54edbb05e","tid":24138,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"香港大農場🤔"},{"pid":"282a4f4cd76d3078fd8bbe071233bcb28ae24e32","tid":24138,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbcae5a49749ca926de49473d859be61ae643a84","tid":24138,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite